{"tid":1543961,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[公投] 要BE WATER定要老解","createTime":"2019-09-05T11:30:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T11:40:02.000Z","uid":153905,"like":25,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6e9cf3718404e3157f1184e2dcc42690e2a64037","tid":1543961,"uid":153905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:30:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1138717819652442&amp;id=387603714763860\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1138717819652442%26id%3D387603714763860&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MLTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=82bb2179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1138717819652442&amp;id=387603714763860</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W0GLAre.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW0GLAre.jpg&h=bf8ec4ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【城論】<br />\n抗爭瓶頸：二揀一，BE WATER定出老解<br />\n文/總編輯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//是次運動亦有以「攬炒」為手段爭取勝利之說，透過街頭激烈抗爭方式迫使中央出動解放軍平亂，促使美國通過《香港人權與民主法案》，繼而用作籌碼爭取中央答應五大訴求。但這抗爭路線是不可能與現時的Be water抗爭模式並存。因為當黑警只要無視守則濫用暴力就能清場，中共根本沒有動用解放軍之必要。我們亦無需假設中共有一天會被激烈示威氣死而出兵，這個想法是輕敵。所以當我們Be water抗爭時，卻許願中共出動解放軍是矛盾的，我們要做的是重擊政權，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">力度超出港共政權負荷</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n當革命是為尋求改變，革命手段及思維亦需不斷改變，切忌奉行信條主義，如「三不」，因而限制抗爭手法，使對手摸熟我方套路。筆者認為即日起所有圍警署行動應徹底be water，設路障而對家列陣警告後便散去，這視為「假動作」，未必能對對方造成傷害，但要令對方每次都齊裝上陣，誤信為一場大仗，卻一無所獲，勞其身心。當減少己方人手損失而對方熟習「假動作」劇本後，再殺對方一個措手不及，把火力集中政權要害，如中聯辦或機場全力打出，要有如2016魚革和7.1衝擊立法會般反擊的覺悟。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不能在攻擊要害時敵進我退，未有達成目標都不要撤退</span></span>。以8.31和9.1為例，縱然對方嚴陣以待也要把中聯辦或機場拿下，令<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">頑強的衝擊超出警方控制範圍以外，才有望見解放軍之希望</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n有人會說天天圍警署是要斷政權六臂，但既然終究都避免不了與黑警衝突，避免不了流血和手足損失，何不go for the head，以政權為目標，在關鍵一役全力重擊，完見老解之心願。//<br />\n<br />\n我要見老解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼續BE WATER<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed6b3a874249080a0f09b39ab829e1b2c5eb2b0","tid":1543961,"uid":153905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:30:58.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"54ff5ad2bac1515450bfe94bb33f9730dbdec207","tid":1543961,"uid":153905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:31:10.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"808f490d61200751dfff9465925d429a01235e72","tid":1543961,"uid":153905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:31:20.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"ef2b859ad295725fa3aa42a6aae7e8c166b9397c","tid":1543961,"uid":274658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:32:00.000Z","msg":"why not both"},{"pid":"7181d3f6485d2f45263d06c3e37e53cbb3b2c1f9","tid":1543961,"uid":153905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:32:07.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"d135850384db94e2175b4497a591b01fdbb15dce","tid":1543961,"uid":153905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef2b859ad295725fa3aa42a6aae7e8c166b9397c","tid":1543961,"uid":274658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:32:00.000Z","msg":"why not both"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:32:53.000Z","msg":"就係根本冇可能both 唔硬碰係唔會見到老解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d1ed6c607bb3a78763182826c3f2ef61c8882af","tid":1543961,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:33:47.000Z","msg":"美國過左再講啦"},{"pid":"0a48084d87b6def4b43711560ac5ab2b940ab21a","tid":1543961,"uid":153905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:34:13.000Z","msg":"冇人想見到流血 但再次次敵進我退係迫唔到老解出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba28d90b360ea623cfcdca833a6cfbb0dd80d805","tid":1543961,"uid"