>\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">9 大核彈<span style=\"font-size: small;\">內容包括</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">：</span></span></span><br />\n(1) 基本法自古以來是中國領土的謬誤<br />\n(2) 中英聯合聲明的謬誤<br />\n(3) 不平等條約無效論是謊言<br />\n(4) 中華民國早已放棄香港的主權<br />\n(5) 中華人民共和國以武力脅迫大英國移交香港主權不合國際法<br />\n(6) 70年代聯合國從非自治領名單剔除香港<br />\n(7) 中英聯合聲明違反住民自決原則<br />\n(8) 香港符合《蒙特維多國家權利及義務公約》中「國家」的定義<br />\n(9) 香港軍事史<br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post！<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港人一定要知！</span></ins></strong></span></span>一定一定要睇！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港史實在此！勿做港豬！想贏就入嚟！</span></span></span></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d3fb2386db31de9c1019523b6d0a2cf03a4901eb","tid":1543961,"uid":153905,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:36:16.000Z","msg":"推 我要見老解 我想摺被<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbcbcb83e75278408767343e714c3e9dd1ebc9aa","tid":1543961,"uid":172192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:36:28.000Z","msg":"不自由 毋寧死<br />\n不惜一切 只要榮光歸香港"},{"pid":"16bc891717db1fe5d0066dcef77fcd2a001f5293","tid":1543961,"uid":153905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1d931c269c5e94b474903901dff6edd086a5804e","tid":1543961,"uid":106326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:36:00.000Z","msg":"Be water 分十次拉1000個人<br />\n老解 一次拉1000個人<br />\n<br />\n老解速戰速決 一場定生死無煩惱 唔洗捉鬼 目標一致<br />\nBe water 每日提心吊膽 遊足十八區 失敗機率次方級遞增"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:36:51.000Z","msg":"ching心水清<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><